claim.claim-text:
1. A method for recording and playing back copies of a program with an interactive media application, the method comprising:
recording multiple copies of a program at different transmission times, each respective copy of the program having respective recording attributes;
receiving a user request to play back the program;
selecting one of the multiple copies of the program; and
playing back at least a portion of the selected copy of the program.

12. A system for recording and playing back copies of a program, the system comprising a recording device and control circuitry, the control circuitry configured to:
record multiple copies of a program at different transmission times, each respective copy of the program having respective recording attributes;
receive a user request to play back the program;
select one of the multiple copies of the program; and
play back at least a portion of the selected copy of the program.
